{
  "video_id": "orumugzJpt0",
  "title": "The reporting system that sexual assault survivors want | Jessica Ladd",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13520.0,
      "end_time": 16936.0,
      "text": "Hannah is excited to be going to college."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16960.0,
      "end_time": 19736.0,
      "text": "She couldn&#39;t wait to get out of her parents&#39; house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19760.0,
      "end_time": 21776.0,
      "text": "to prove to them that she&#39;s an adult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21800.0,
      "end_time": 24480.0,
      "text": "and to prove to her new friends that she belongs."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25360.0,
      "end_time": 26936.0,
      "text": "She heads to a campus party"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26960.0,
      "end_time": 29496.0,
      "text": "where she sees a guy that she has a crush on."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29520.0,
      "end_time": 30880.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s call him Mike."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32439.0,
      "end_time": 36519.0,
      "text": "The next day, Hannah wakes up with a pounding headache."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37280.0,
      "end_time": 39960.0,
      "text": "She can only remember the night in flashes."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40480.0,
      "end_time": 42175.0,
      "text": "But what she does remember is"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42200.0,
      "end_time": 45400.0,
      "text": "throwing up in the hall outside Mike&#39;s room"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46440.0,
      "end_time": 49536.0,
      "text": "and staring at the wall silently while he was inside her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49560.0,
      "end_time": 50840.0,
      "text": "wanting it to stop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51520.0,
      "end_time": 53480.0,
      "text": "then shakily stumbling home."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54856.0,
      "end_time": 56856.0,
      "text": "She doesn&#39;t feel good about what happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56880.0,
      "end_time": 60600.0,
      "text": "but she thinks, \"Maybe this is just what sex in college is?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61840.0,
      "end_time": 66560.0,
      "text": "One in five women and one in 13 men will be sexually assaulted"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66800.0,
      "end_time": 70200.0,
      "text": "at some point during their college career in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71520.0,
      "end_time": 75936.0,
      "text": "Less than 10 percent will ever report their assault to their school"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75960.0,
      "end_time": 77455.0,
      "text": "or to the police."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77480.0,
      "end_time": 82400.0,
      "text": "And those who do, on average, wait 11 months to make the report."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 84400.0,
      "end_time": 87736.0,
      "text": "Hannah initially just feels like dealing with what happened on her own."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 87760.0,
      "end_time": 90336.0,
      "text": "But when she sees Mike taking girls home from parties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 90360.0,
      "end_time": 91600.0,
      "text": "she&#39;s worried about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92600.0,
      "end_time": 94856.0,
      "text": "After graduation, Hannah learns"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94880.0,
      "end_time": 99920.0,
      "text": "that she was one of five women who Mike did the exact same thing to."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100840.0,
      "end_time": 103256.0,
      "text": "And this is not an unlikely scenario"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 103280.0,
      "end_time": 106336.0,
      "text": "because 90 percent of sexual assaults"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106360.0,
      "end_time": 108600.0,
      "text": "are committed by repeat offenders."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 109160.0,
      "end_time": 110816.0,
      "text": "But with such low reporting rates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 110840.0,
      "end_time": 114656.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s fairly unlikely that even repeat perpetrators will be reported,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114680.0,
      "end_time": 117216.0,
      "text": "much less anything happen if they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 117240.0,
      "end_time": 122375.0,
      "text": "In fact, only six percent of assaults reported to the police"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122400.0,
      "end_time": 125280.0,
      "text": "end with the assailant spending a single day in prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 125680.0,
      "end_time": 130480.0,
      "text": "Meaning, there&#39;s a 99 percent chance that they&#39;ll get away with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 131400.0,
      "end_time": 134816.0,
      "text": "This means there&#39;s practically no deterrent to assault"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 134840.0,
      "end_time": 136320.0,
      "text": "in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 138160.0,
      "end_time": 141496.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m an infectious disease epidemiologist by training."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 141520.0,
      "end_time": 144616.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m interested in systems and networks"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 144640.0,
      "end_time": 148640.0,
      "text": "and where we can concentrate our resources to do the most good."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 149200.0,
      "end_time": 154320.0,
      "text": "So this, to me, is a tragic but a solvable problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 155280.0,
      "end_time": 159416.0,
      "text": "So when the issue of campus assault started hitting the news a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 159440.0,
      "end_time": 162816.0,
      "text": "it felt like a unique opportunity to make a change."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 162840.0,
      "end_time": 164400.0,
      "text": "And so we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 164560.0,
      "end_time": 167336.0,
      "text": "We started by talking to college survivors."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 167360.0,
      "end_time": 170360.0,
      "text": "And what they wish they&#39;d had in college is pretty simple;"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 170880.0,
      "end_time": 172416.0,
      "text": "they wanted a website,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 172440.0,
      "end_time": 174576.0,
      "text": "one they could use at the time and place"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 174600.0,
      "end_time": 176400.0,
      "text": "that felt safest to them"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 176800.0,
      "end_time": 180776.0,
      "text": "with clearly written information about their reporting options,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 180800.0,
      "end_time": 183936.0,
      "text": "with the ability to electronically report their assault,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 183960.0,
      "end_time": 185576.0,
      "text": "rather than having the first step"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 185600.0,
      "end_time": 188480.0,
      "text": "to go in and talk to someone who may or may not believe them."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 189800.0,
      "end_time": 192376.0,
      "text": "With the option to create a secure, timestamped document"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 192400.0,
      "end_time": 193896.0,
      "text": "of what happened to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 193920.0,
      "end_time": 196959.0,
      "text": "preserving evidence even if they don&#39;t want to report yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 197560.0,
      "end_time": 200536.0,
      "text": "And lastly, and perhaps most critically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 200560.0,
      "end_time": 202576.0,
      "text": "with the ability to report their assault"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 202600.0,
      "end_time": 206239.0,
      "text": "only if someone else reported the same assailant."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 206920.0,
      "end_time": 210550.0,
      "text": "You see, knowing that you weren&#39;t the only one changes everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 210800.0,
      "end_time": 212416.0,
      "text": "It changes the way you frame your own experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 212440.0,
      "end_time": 214896.0,
      "text": "it changes the way you think about your perpetrator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 214920.0,
      "end_time": 216736.0,
      "text": "it means that if you do come forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216760.0,
      "end_time": 219799.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll have someone else&#39;s back and they&#39;ll have yours."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 220840.0,
      "end_time": 223336.0,
      "text": "We created a website that actually does this"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223360.0,
      "end_time": 226376.0,
      "text": "and we launched it [...] in August,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226400.0,
      "end_time": 228000.0,
      "text": "on two college campuses."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 228600.0,
      "end_time": 231495.0,
      "text": "And we included a unique matching system"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 231520.0,
      "end_time": 234456.0,
      "text": "where if Mike&#39;s first victim had come forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 234480.0,
      "end_time": 237256.0,
      "text": "saved her record, entered into the matching system"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 237280.0,
      "end_time": 238536.0,
      "text": "and named Mike,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 238560.0,
      "end_time": 240936.0,
      "text": "and Mike&#39;s second victim had done the same thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 240960.0,
      "end_time": 242616.0,
      "text": "a few months later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 242640.0,
      "end_time": 243976.0,
      "text": "they would have matched"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 244000.0,
      "end_time": 247496.0,
      "text": "and the verified contact information of both survivors"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 247520.0,
      "end_time": 250256.0,
      "text": "would have been sent to the authorities at the same time"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 250280.0,
      "end_time": 252320.0,
      "text": "for investigation and follow up."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 253600.0,
      "end_time": 257296.0,
      "text": "If a system like this had existed for Hannah and her peers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 257320.0,
      "end_time": 259856.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s more likely that they would have reported,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 259880.0,
      "end_time": 261656.0,
      "text": "that they would have been believed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 261680.0,
      "end_time": 263936.0,
      "text": "and that Mike would have been kicked off campus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 263960.0,
      "end_time": 266960.0,
      "text": "gone to jail, or at least gotten the help that he needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 267920.0,
      "end_time": 271416.0,
      "text": "And if we were able to stop repeat offenders like Mike"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 271440.0,
      "end_time": 275560.0,
      "text": "after just their second assault following a match,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 275800.0,
      "end_time": 277695.0,
      "text": "survivors like Hannah would never even be assaulted"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 277720.0,
      "end_time": 279000.0,
      "text": "in the first place."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 279760.0,
      "end_time": 283856.0,
      "text": "We could prevent 59 percent of sexual assaults"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 283880.0,
      "end_time": 286960.0,
      "text": "just by stopping repeat perpetrators earlier on."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 288800.0,
      "end_time": 290776.0,
      "text": "And because we&#39;re creating a real deterrent to assault,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 290800.0,
      "end_time": 292936.0,
      "text": "for perhaps the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 292960.0,
      "end_time": 296320.0,
      "text": "maybe the Mikes of the world would never even try to assault anyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 298640.0,
      "end_time": 300616.0,
      "text": "The type of system I&#39;m describing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 300640.0,
      "end_time": 303150.0,
      "text": "the type of system that survivors want"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 303400.0,
      "end_time": 305576.0,
      "text": "is a type of information escrow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 305600.0,
      "end_time": 308816.0,
      "text": "meaning an entity that holds on to information for you"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308840.0,
      "end_time": 311296.0,
      "text": "and only releases it to a third party"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 311320.0,
      "end_time": 313896.0,
      "text": "when certain pre-agreed upon conditions are met,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 313920.0,
      "end_time": 315120.0,
      "text": "such as a match."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 315600.0,
      "end_time": 319336.0,
      "text": "The application that we built is for college campuses."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 319360.0,
      "end_time": 322416.0,
      "text": "But the same type of system could be used in the military"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 322440.0,
      "end_time": 323840.0,
      "text": "or even the workplace."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 325720.0,
      "end_time": 328256.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have to live in a world"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 328280.0,
      "end_time": 331440.0,
      "text": "where 99 percent of rapists get away with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 332120.0,
      "end_time": 333536.0,
      "text": "We can create one"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 333560.0,
      "end_time": 336496.0,
      "text": "where those who do wrong are held accountable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 336520.0,
      "end_time": 339936.0,
      "text": "where survivors get the support and justice they deserve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 339960.0,
      "end_time": 342856.0,
      "text": "where the authorities get the information they need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 342880.0,
      "end_time": 344776.0,
      "text": "and where there&#39;s a real deterrent"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 344800.0,
      "end_time": 348440.0,
      "text": "to violating the rights of another human being."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 349120.0,
      "end_time": 350336.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 350360.0,
      "end_time": 353320.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}